{"type": "article", "id": 11400, "title": "Dalt储存单元", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-30T12:00:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115257MfCZp4YQK0aR1noj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t去年，宜家发布了约 51 件收纳品类的产品。而<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2015/06/28/dalt-storage-system-jordi-iranzo-pulley-ceiling/\" target=\"_blank\">根据一份研究表明</a>，有 1/5 的城市居民居住空间不足 30 平方米。Jordi Iranzo 是今年毕业于德国哈勒艺术和设计学院（Burg Giebichenstein University of Art and Design）的一名设计专业的学生，最近他就设计了一款专为狭小空间而生的储存单元 Dalt ,可以悬挂在天花板上，不占用任何的地面空间。用户可以将其当作是一个浮动在床头或是写字桌前的储存装置，既可以收纳一些衣物、杂物，也可以放置零食饮料等小物。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115252lCzEgma1owiWRTG8.jpg\" width=\"467\" height=\"603\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"1.29122056\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021152548nzyCajg0WYXZmMi.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"639\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.36538462\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115255hM9dtIY2XSVkawNG.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"702\" title=\"4\" alt=\"4\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115255a9wNXoEL6O3gi0Um.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"702\" title=\"6\" alt=\"6\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115256kaAg8so5cj1Iv0Ue.jpg\" width=\"468\" height=\"702\" title=\"7\" alt=\"7\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}